            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I had the unfortunate destiny of studying in this school from 1984 (roll number 64 when this was known as cca and location was different) Unfortunate because JS sir and Neena mam, i still respect you, but your physical abuses still show signs on damage on my phyche. You did not inspire me unfortunately and I as a little child looked up to you as my inspiration but you failed. You did not know how to treat little kids with care, but you just doled out physical punishment which nobody does that to animals today. As a result of these experiences, I put my kids in schools where this is not the case, and make sure my kids are not touched. I am 42 but I cannot forget such the fear and regression induced by your savage behavior, once my wife had a chance to speak to neena mam as she is a teacher and neena mam recalled me as someone \"who would not do homework and get ears pulled\" in a derogatory way. let me tell you that I am a much better man not because of your school, which i left in 1991 but due to my own making and I wish I never came across your school. But what to do, i was such ill failed that you came to my home, to my grand father begging for my admission because your school was new and he listened. Hope you have stopped this nonsense now, May you live a blessed life!",
